{"tid":2092462,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（唔係唔理香港）美國單日新增近5.5萬人染疫 創全球紀錄","createTime":"2020-07-03T08:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T08:38:14.000Z","uid":66087,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"720a35b174408d786b6bbdf51a8271575b5bd54f","tid":2092462,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:28:12.000Z","msg":"路透社報導，全美各地過去一週的感染人數激增，使得總統川普（Donald Trump）的防疫因應遭到嚴格檢視，一些州也暫緩解封計畫。<br />\n<br />\n截至今晚，美國單日新增感染人數為5萬4879人，超越巴西在6月19日創下的單日新增5萬4711人感染紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n根據統計，就在約2週前，美國每天新增約2萬2000例病例，如今連續7天每天新增超過4萬人感染，且連續3天的新增病例數都破紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透社分析，和截至6月初的2週相比，美國50州中有37州在過去14天的感染人數持續上升。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202007030058.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202007030058.aspx&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=500e9657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202007030058.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"f21bdf678a6f5c30511e8f7e76fc36913ecb0c6a","tid":2092462,"uid":66087,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"出面幾個post係度鬧侵唔做嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但有冇唸過其實美國自己都好大件事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855d5880faceec30730194053e7b186460b1071b","tid":2092462,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"係咪又係民主黨洲份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bbf306ed73f715bff50de39ae3599d7a131bf8","tid":2092462,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"855d5880faceec30730194053e7b186460b1071b","tid":2092462,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"係咪又係民主黨洲份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"Florida 最多，搖擺州份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162ad73c6f4aec76bad43aa68bc528ce739f4e73","tid":2092462,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"根據路透社分析，和截至6月初的2週相比，美國50州中有37州在過去14天的感染人數持續上升。<br />\n<br />\n佛羅里達州今天新增逾1萬人感染，是迄今單日新增感染人數最多的州。擁有2100萬人口的佛州，單日新增病例數，高於歐洲疫情高峰期的任何一國每日確診病例數。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家過敏與傳染病研究院（NIAID）院長佛奇（Anthony Fauci）本週稍早警告，如果國內未能採取措施讓疫情趨緩，全國每日新增病例數恐達10萬。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透社分析，美國國內上週篩檢復陽的比例是7%，高於前一週的5%；亞利桑那州上週的篩檢陽性比例是24%，佛州16%，內華達州、南卡羅來納州和德州皆為15%。（譯者：陳怡君/核稿：嚴思祺）"},{"pid":"9163ab01b3744dddc94335077069ed2236b0c6ef","tid":2092462,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"不過係後生輕症居多<br />\n死亡率好底"},{"pid":"3b58f348e468a98bdccaa0d8f20d04d4cd454540","tid":2092462,"uid":333199,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"其實係咪會滅國....美國"},{"pid":"8ed1acef8990d902cbb4db4fb7b9a743afdf7157","tid":2092462,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9163ab01b3744dddc94335077069ed2236b0c6ef","tid":2092462,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"不過係後生輕症居多<br />\n死亡率好底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"Around 2-3%，可以接受"},{"pid":"15565c58412cb2ad236eb998d51d5296b2548960","tid":2092462,"uid":121146,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"大豆侵應該都玩完  佢係疫情上事實係處理得好撚差"},{"pid":"6250906f1d01f757047b8c9a231d614c6ae40d73","tid":2092462,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"BLM herd immunity?"},{"pid":"2a444ce99979318fba99e1f0369dbf5ba45f39ad","tid":2092462,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"162ad73c6f4aec76bad43aa68bc528ce739f4e73